<h2>SSE Streams</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>GET /api/daemon-events</code> — daemon-wide event stream with <code>stream:hello</code> snapshot on connect.</li>
<li><code>GET /api/events/:runId</code> — session-specific event stream with <code>stream:hello</code> snapshot on connect.</li>
</ul>
<p>Use <code>buildPath(pattern, params)</code> from <code>@eforge-build/client</code> to resolve <code>:param</code> placeholders.</p>
